On January 1, 2006 Fexhe-le-Haut-Clocher had a total population of 3,019. The total area is 19.25 km² which gives a [[population density]] of 157 inhabitants per km². ==References== {{reflist}} {{Liege municipalities}} [[Category:Municipalities of Liège (province)]] {{Liege-geo-stub}}
